cavalier about?

01:21:57.956 --> 01:22:00.708
Those people, they're not
your friends, Lizzie.

01:22:00.708 --> 01:22:03.919
Nonsense.
They aren't here
because they like you.

01:22:03.919 --> 01:22:05.963
You're a carnival attraction
to them.

01:22:05.963 --> 01:22:07.506
